^ C. Amsler et al. (Particle Data Group). Review of Particle Physics – Pentaquarks (PDF). Physics Letters B. 2008, 667: 1. Bibcode:2008PhLB..667....1P. doi:10.1016/j.physletb.2008.07.018. 
^ Mysterious Subatomic Particle May Represent Exotic New Form of Matter










